1963 BALLON D'OR
The 1963 Ballon d'Or , given to the best football player in Europe as judged by a panel of sports journalists from UEFA member countries , was awarded to Lev Yashin , the first , and as of 2018 , the only goalkeeper to win this award .
Also he became the first Soviet and Russian national to win the trophy .
